downloadTitle: Microsoft Lync 2010 Adoption and Training Kit: Web Banners
downloadDescription: This zipped file contains sample web banners for Microsoft Lync 2010.
detailsSection: These sample web banners can be used on your internal web sites or other awareness materials during rollout and adoption of Microsoft Lync 2010.
systemRequirementsSection: Programs compatible with Portable Network Graphics (PNG) files
installInstructionSection: To install the download, save the zipped file to a directory on your computer. After you save it, unzip it by right-clicking the file name, selecting Extract All, selecting a destination where you want the extracted files to reside, and then clicking Extract. To remove the download, delete the file from directory where you saved it.
